description: Modern apartment on the 13th floor in an apartment building.  A huge balcony guarantees a magnificent view of the entire city, and the flat itself is only 10 min by walk to the Wrocław Market Square.The spaceI have furnished the apartment to ensure the best possible comfort for my guests.  Despite the building's location with the very centre, the 13th floor ensures quiet and relaxation. The living room in grey, beige and white with designer elements such as the chandelier creates a cosy and elegant interior. The large corner sofa bed provides sleeping space for additional guests. Right next to it you will find the kitchenette with all cooking accessories such as oven, dishwasher, electric hob and Nespresso capsule machine. In the bedroom you will find a bed prepared for you, and for your convenience I have provided bedside tables and pendant bedside lamps. In the bathroom you will find a bathtub with shower function, a wide washbasin and a washing machine. I will provide a set of towels for you and each guest. I have also provided a laundry dryer, ironing board and iron.  The apartment has a huge corner balcony overlooking the Oder River and Wrocław.Guest accessMy guests have exclusive use of the entire apartment and access to the viewing terrace on the 18th floor of the building, where they can enjoy the wonderful view of Wroclaw.You can rent a parking space in underground garage, the cost is 60PLN per day.Other things to noteI issue VAT invoices.

description: The apartment is close to the city center, which would allow you to get quickly to the heart of magical city of dwarfs. At the same time the apartment is located in quiet area, which would help you rest and prepare for the next day of adventure. We would welcome you with a bottle of water and sweets. Enjoy coffee from the coffee machine in the mornings and Netflix in the evenings. For your convenience there are small lamps by the bed which can be used for reading.Guest accessThe whole apartment is for you own use: bedroom, separate kitchen and private bathroom.Other things to noteThe apartment has been fitted with a smartlock, therefore you will receive your own unlocking code immediately after reservation has been confirmed. You will also be able to open the apartment with your own smartphone. Thanks to that you will not need to wait for host to provide you with the keys or specify exact arrival time - the code and app will be active throughout time off your stay. You will also not need to worry about losing the apartment keys, which usually incurs extra fees. Your safety is our top priority so even though local regulation does not require it we have fitted the apartment with smoke and carbon monoxide alarms. We also ensure that your bed sheets and towels are clean and fresh.During your stay, you can use private car park available. Usually there is plenty of spaces available but in rare cases you may need to park on the road nearby - this is also free of charge.The apartment is suitable for 2 adults (1 double bed) or family with 1 child up to 4 years old.  Tourist bed for child can be provided for one-time fee of 100 zl. Please contact us before you book the place so we can send you updated offer with the fee included.

A hotel restaurant is available in the building. A great advantage is the proximity of 270 m to the Main Railway Station, which is a very attractive location for travellers. There are two parks nearby - the Nicolaus Copernicus Park and the Czesław Niemen Park. description: ★ Easy self check-in & check-out★ Microapartments in the center of Wrocław★ In a private tenament building on Podwale 36b Str.★ Size: 15 - 20 m²★ 120 m from the Renoma shopping center★ 1 km to the main railway station★ 700 m to the Market Square★ Pets welcome (a fee applies)★ Charming vintage decor★ Kitchenettes with essentials★ Wi-Fi★ TV★ Cosmetics set, towels, bed linen★ VAT-invoice (at request)The spaceIMPORTANT NOTE: Please note that this listing advertizes three apartments. The apartments all have the same size and standards but may differ in details.BUILDING AND AREA DESCRIPTION:These studio apartaments are situated on the first floor lin a four-story building in the very center of Wrocław. The building is located just beside the Old Town Promenade and the City Moat! The area is very well connected with the main attractions of Wrocław - the Old Market Square is within an 8-minute walk, the Tumski Bridge and the Słodowa Island are within a 6-minute drive. The Main Railway Station is very close to the accommodation - only 13 minutes on foot! There are numerous cafes and restaurants in the area, representing the rich gastronomic offer of Wrocław. The accomodation is also surrounded by the shopping centers: the Renoma Shopping Center (100 m), Arcady Wrocławskie (550 m), and Galeria Dominikańska (1 km). The neighborhood is also known for the cultural centers and facilities. Art lovers will appreciate the proximity of the Opera (230 m), many theatres, and the arthouse cinema New Horizons movie theatre (800 m). The central location of the apartment also provides proximity to many bus and streetcar stops, which will facilitate access to other districts of Wrocław.APARTMENT DESCRIPTION:The studio apartments can accommodate two people and are perfect for a couple or an individual stay. They consist of a living room with a small kitchenette and a bathroom with a shower. There is also a common area on the ground floor near the entrance. The décor of studios reflects the historical character of the district, created by charming elements such as dark wood shutters and frames, stained glass windows and a beautiful wooden staircase. The result is a revamped vintage style, combining new and retro furniture with many modern conveniences. The amenities include multimedia (tv set andfree Wi-Fi connection) and a comprehensive range of household appliances (microwave, hairdryer, electric kettle). Please note that there is only electric heating available.LIVING Room: Double Sofabed, Tv, coffee table,KITCHENETTE:Microwave, electric kettle, set of dishes, cutlery, wine glassesBATHROOM: Shower, toilet, sink, mirror, towels, hair dryerMULTIMEDIA:TV, Wi-FiPETS: Pets are accepted for an additional fee.PARKING: Public on-street parking (additional charges may apply).The property has ENERGY PERFORMANCE CERTIFICATEOther things to noteOptional services- Cot/Crib: Price: PLN 50.00 per day.- Pet: Price: PLN 100.00 per booking.
